♪The night wind blows, my eyes reddened♪

739
00:35:08,860 --> 00:35:15,460
♪Thoughts sink below the vast ocean♪

740
00:35:16,260 --> 00:35:23,460
♪The night wind blows, disorienting me♪

741
00:35:23,460 --> 00:35:29,380
♪Those who go and never return,
they sadden me♪

742
00:35:29,380 --> 00:35:33,420
♪I'm lost♪

743
