♪Make a wish,
like it's going to come true♪

744
00:35:52,700 --> 00:36:00,260
♪Time will convey your answer♪

745
00:36:00,260 --> 00:36:07,700
♪You say you want
to search the distance♪

746
00:36:07,700 --> 00:36:14,340
♪Smiling, I hope everything
will remain as it is♪

747
00:36:15,140 --> 00:36:22,020
♪The Milky Way
keeps memories of the past♪

748
00:36:22,020 --> 00:36:29,620
♪Every wish is a star that still shines♪

749
00:36:30,020 --> 00:36:37,180
♪Whenever I feel down and helpless♪

750
00:36:37,180 --> 00:36:43,620
♪I look at it, and everything
